# =============================================================================
# Evaluation_neuron_interpretability
#
# Version control: Python source (.py), notebooks (.ipynb), project config
# (requirements*.txt, README.md), and small result summaries (metrics CSV/JSON,
# aggregate plots). Exclude virtual environments, raw datasets, model weights,
# and multi-MB sweep exports.
#
# GitHub hard limit: 100 MB per file. Sizes below are approximate (local disk).
# =============================================================================

# --- Virtual environments (never commit) ---
.venv/
venv/
venv_*/
env/
ENV/
.conda/
venv_evaluation_interpretability/

# --- Python / Jupyter ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- OS / editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Upstream VEGA (clone locally; see README) ---
# Ignore all contents of vega/ except PLACEHOLDER (empty marker for GitHub).
vega/*
!vega/
!vega/PLACEHOLDER

# --- Raw datasets and numeric arrays (download or regenerate locally) ---
# pbmc_data/ holds PBMC_8K_expression.h5 (~97 MB total)
pbmc_data/
# data_trial_v6/*.npy: dataset_X.npy, concept_activities.npy (~18 MB)
data_trial_v6/*.npy
*.h5
*.h5ad
*.npy
*.npz

# --- Model checkpoints (retrain with run_vega_fcn_sweep.py / train_vega_pbmc.py) ---
# vega_fcn_sweep/fcn_*/vega2_*.pt (~23 MB each); plots_vega_simulation/vega2_beta.pt (~6 MB)
*.pt
*.pth
*.pkl
*.parquet

# --- Run logs ---
# e.g. vega_fcn_sweep/sweep.log (~450 KB)
*.log

# --- Large CSV exports: neuron-simulation probability sweeps (too big for GitHub) ---
# plots_trial_v6_exp/probabilities_overlap_threshold_sweep.csv (~485 MB)
# plots_trial_v6_uniform/probabilities_overlap_threshold_sweep.csv (~482 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_overlap_threshold_sweep.csv
# plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_K_sweep.csv (~135 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_K_sweep.csv
# plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_overlap_sweep.csv (~64 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_overlap_sweep.csv
# plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_M_sweep.csv (~58 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_M_sweep.csv
# plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_beta_sweep.csv (~36 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/probabilities_beta_sweep.csv
# plots_trial_v6_*/overlap_regime_pairwise_values.csv (~5 MB)
plots_trial_v6_*/overlap_regime_pairwise_values.csv

# --- Small results kept (not ignored) ---
# vega_fcn_sweep/aggregate/per_neuron_metrics.csv (~2 MB)
# vega_fcn_sweep/fcn_*/interpretability_metrics.csv (~136 KB each)
# vega_fcn_sweep/aggregate/*.png, fcn_*/04_reconstruction_test.png (~112-196 KB)
# vega_fcn_sweep/fcn_*/metrics.json, training_info.txt
# plots_dcorr_v2_*/distance_corr_*.csv (~170-280 KB)
# plots_vega_simulation/metrics.json, *.png
# data_trial_v6/concept_mapping.json
